<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Kingsman</title>
    <!-- FONTS -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Montserrat:300,400,700" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
    <%- include('./partials/head.ejs'); -%>
  </head>
  <body>
    <!-- ====== TOP HEADER BAR ====== -->
    <div class="header">
      <!-- title -->
      <div class="header-title">
        <img src="homework/kingsman_auth/public/img/logo.png" alt="kingsman logo">
        <h1>KINGSMAN TAILOR</h1>
      </div>
      <!-- navigation -->
      <div class="header-nav">
        <% if(currentUser) { %>
          <ul>
            <li>
              Welcome, <%= currentUser.username %>!
            </li>
            <li>
              <a class="waves-effect waves-light btn" href="/room">fitting room three</a>
            </li>
            <!-- add your form button to log out here -->
            <li>
              <form action="/sessions?_method=DELETE" method="POST">
                <input type="submit" value="Logout" class="waves-effect waves-light btn"/>
              </form>
            </li>
          </ul>
        <% } else { %>
        <ul>
          <!-- add your link to create a user here -->
          <li>
            <a class="waves-effect waves-light btn" href="/users/new">Sign Up</a></h2>
          </li>
          <!-- add your link to the log in page here -->
          <li>
            <a class="waves-effect waves-light btn" href="/sessions/new">Log In</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <% } %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- ===== MAIN SPLASH PAGE CONTENT ===== -->
    <div class="main">
      <!-- image -->
      <img src="homework/kingsman_auth/public/img/splash.jpg" alt="splash image of kingsman display window"/>
      <!-- about -->
      <div class="main-abt">
        <h1>the modern gentleman's armour: a suit</h1>
        As Hemingway said, "There is nothing noble in being superior to your fellow man. True nobility is being superior to your former self.""
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
